cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DB

This paper is about document filtering, which is a task related to information retrieval (IR). Therefore, cs.IR is the most likely sub-category. The paper also deals with natural language processing (NLP) tasks such as entity recognition and relation extraction, which are typically covered in cs.CL. The proposed method involves machine learning techniques, which are covered in cs.LG and cs.AI. Finally, the paper deals with data management and storage, which are covered in cs.DB.
